{"metadata":{"role":"collectionGroup","title":"TokensProvider Implementations","roleHeading":"API Collection","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider\/TokensProvider-Implementations"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider"]]},"kind":"article","topicSections":[{"anchor":"Instance-Methods","generated":true,"title":"Instance Methods","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider\/checkInstances(count:for:)"]}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemequantityinputcomponenttokensprovider\/tokensprovider-implementations"]}],"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","title":"Theme Orange","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of quantity input","type":